description:
THE DREDD MOVIE SEQUEL COMIC IS BACK IN A TWO-PART SPECIAL!

Judge Dredd heads beyond the walls of Mega-City One and into the irradiated wasteland known as The Cursed Earth in search of a deadly assassin, who has been infiltrating the metropolis and mercilessly executing particular targets. Just what is the truth behind the murders? ‘Dust’ is the latest comic-book sequel to the critically-acclaimed cult movie DREDD, from series writer Arthur Wyatt and JUDGE DREDD and DOCTOR WHO artist Ben Willsher!
